     </S>
     <S id="S3">
          <FORM>3 Annata ni-tpapænh ta ti Petrus, ki Pahtatæutæu'-hanap-pa ka saaisat, ka ni-ierrouatou ra-vak.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S5">
          <FORM>4 Ra darouha kanna ta ni-ma hkaulla si-houm: ra Pahta-tæu'han-appa ka sasisat ta ni-si-houm fsi-ourou mt'ægh ti Pe-trus-an, ka si-ouro'-en tyn mou-koua tou ravak.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S7">
          <FORM>5 Irou ka mæ'æu-sousou, ni-kyt-t'an tyn ta atta-kou-an ka æ-it, ra assi ni-mou-rbo' hynna.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S9">
          <FORM>6 Ka ni-ierroua-appa ta ti Simon Petrus mæ-æ-ugh tyni-n, ka ni-mou-rbou ta teni tou ravak, kmytta ki atta-kou'an ka a-it.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S11">
          <FORM>7 Ka na ta t'oupou ki moul-la ka ni-atta-halap-pen tou voun-go tyn assi ni-atta-sal-lan ki æ-it, ra ni-atta''-1bæh -enappa matta-'kkurik tou pani ki i-tou-kou'-an.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S13">
          <FORM>8 Annata ni-mou-rbo-appa ta Pahtatæutæu-'han ka saasat ka ni-si-ourou mou-kouatou r'avak, ka ni-k'yt-tan tyn, ka ni-tna'-'mfsing-appa.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S15">
          <FORM>9 Nda asfi-appa-nein 'ou-mhg'an ta na Sa-Soulat, ka lyk-kough-eih tyn æhpit ki ni-ka pa-tei-an.</FORM>
     </S>
